answer: Multiple services offer digital reading subscriptions at different monthly prices, e.g., $7.99 for Kobo Plus Read/Listen, $9.99 for Kindle Unlimited, $11.99 for Kobo Plus Read, $11.99/month for Kindle Unlimited, $12.99/month for Readly, $19.99/year for PressReader, $24.99/year for Epic, and $99/year for Pocketmags.
